        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "Classify the user message into one of these intents:\n- greeting: greetings, hello, hi, how are you\n- company_query: questions about company services, solutions, technologies, projects, support, company information\n- job_query: questions about job openings, hiring, careers, internships, positions, roles, skills required, how to apply\n- unclear: vague, incomplete, or ambiguous messages\n- unrelated: spam, abuse, rude messages, or topics unrelated to company or jobs\n\nClassify accurately and return confidence score."
        }
